; Exports symbols from C API DLL or executables when C API is statically linked.
; The list of symbols here doesn't cover all symbols of C API, but added as
; needed when linker fails to find symbols. Currently, they are used by
; litert_lm_main.exe when --define=litert_link_capi_so=true and by
; libLiteRtWebGpuAccelerator.dll when --define=resolve_symbols_from_exec=true.

